text: Oj Igmane (Oh, Igman) is the second release by Bosnian folk singer Zehra Deović. It was released 2 October 1963 through the label Jugoton. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== *Narodni Ansambl Ismeta Alajbegovića "Šerbe" – ensemble ==References== Category:1963 EPs Category:Zehra Deović albums Category:Jugoton EPs
